title: Casio Men's AE-2100W-4AVCF Digital 10-Year Battery Digital Display Quartz Orange Watch
feature: World time round watch with 31 time zones featuring 1/100-second stopwatch, countdown timer, five daily alarms, full auto-calendar, and 12/24-hour time format
48 mm stainless steel case with mineral dial window
10-year battery-driven quartz movement with digital display
Water resistant to 200 m (660 ft): In general, suitable for professional marine activity and serious surface water sports, but not scuba diving
description: World time round watch with 31 time zones featuring 1/100-second stopwatch, countdown timer, five daily alarms, full auto-calendar, and 12/24-hour time format Go 10 years without changing a battery! Advanced technology extends the battery life in this AE2100W series so you can enjoy the timekeeping and other functions for a decade without shopping for a new battery! In addition to the extended battery life you can also enjoy the World Map, LC Analog Display along with being 200M water resistant. You will also find the 24 hour stopwatch and timer useful for your daily exercise and fitness needs.
